sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor AT as Attendee
    participant EP as Event Page
    participant DJ as Django Web App
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    AT ->> EP: Open Event Page
    EP ->> DJ: Request Event Details
    DJ ->> DB: Query Event by ID
    DB -->> DJ: Return Event Data
    DJ -->> EP: Send Event Details
    EP -->> AT: Display Event Info

    Note right of EP: Event details shown include:<br/>• Title<br/>• Organizer<br/>• Description<br/>• Venue<br/>• Media (if any)<br/>• Dates/Times<br/>• Ticket types with prices<br/>• Fees/Taxes note
